            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Please don’t waste your money if you both are working parent. The teachers have their own favourites and highly unprofessional when it comes to feedback sharing. We sent our child thinking it’s one of the best! But looks like it’s was opened for group of frens.\nThe teacher never informed us any progress or work on area feedback once we switched to bus services. Nor we were informed that the session is complete.\nJust Pooja is fine as a teacher and Sukruti has no interest if your kid doesn’t manage to charm her. She will give the reason that I handle 8 kids without a didi! U paying high amount of your hard earn money to hear such clichés responses. I would suggest productive mind or pathways or nanhe Kadam over this school! Please don’t waste your money here !",
          "publisher": {
