            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "SIS PREP has played a crucial role in the holistic development of my daughter. The balance of academics, extracurricular activities, and social skills development is just right. However, I would like to see more emphasis on developing a love for nature and outdoor activities. But overall, this is the best preschool in Gurgaon that I have come across.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
