          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I appreciate the emphasis SIS PREP places on healthy eating habits. My son, who is a picky eater, now enjoys the organic, vegetarian meals provided by the school. When I first visited SIS PREP, I was skeptical about enrolling my child. However, after 3-4 weeks, my child has become more open with others and has developed improved social skills. The teachers here handle all situations very professionally.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
