            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter has always been a creative soul, and SIS PREP has provided her with the perfect platform to express her creativity. The arts and crafts, music, and storytelling activities have been a hit with her. I just wish there were more opportunities for parents to be involved in these activities.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
